          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1623678530066-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the turkey mixture thickens, return the<strong> drained potatoes & carrots</strong> to a low heat with 10g <span class=\"text-danger\">[20g]</span> <strong>butter</strong>, a splash of <strong>milk </strong>and a pinch of<strong> salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Mash until smooth</p><p>Tip: Don't worry if your carrot doesn't get completely smooth, it will add a nice texture to your mash!</p>",
      "order": 5,
